.Dd April 23, 2026
.Dt MAT_CRITICAL 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm Mat_Critical
.Nd Logs a critical error message and returns.
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Fd #include <matio.h>
.Ft void
.Fo Mat_Critical
.Fa "const char *format"
.Fa "..."
.Fc
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn Mat_Critical
function formats and emits a critical error message through the active matio
logging callback, then returns to the caller.
Use
.Fn Mat_Error
when the program should terminate.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr Mat_Error 3 ,
.Xr Mat_Warning 3